tion_qck_tjl_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d964863e78\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfw1705577424699.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfw1705577424699.html\" title=\"Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications.\">Menu Objects</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615570\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615570\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Font Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Font Name of a logical font to be used for menus, as specified in the initialization file. If not specified, the Windows system default font is used. This property can only be set in the .ini file. For valid values, see the usys.ini file. [application] menu=umenu(Font= LogicalFont ) Copy Example: Setting the Font Used for Menus ;usys.ini file [application] menu=umenu(font=SansMedium) Copy Applies To Menu Objects Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}